{"tid":813684,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"港女有三樣嘢真係無得改","createTime":"2018-09-10T15:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T06:09:12.000Z","uid":195323,"like":28,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7103a3a82c7a4a9033900a40d2143a6a2bf620ad","tid":813684,"uid":195323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:46:05.000Z","msg":"港女有三樣嘢真係會令男士卻步：脾氣差、視野窄、唔運動，或者仲可以咁講：冇內涵！<br />\n啲90,00後要求男朋友米8<br />\n你自己好高咩？比米8有鬼用<br />\n真係鐘意你講咩身高！<br />\n<br />\n不過掉轉個問題嚟睇，女人揀男人應該就簡單得多，認為錢可解釋一切！所以港女咪以為自己「高學歷、高職位、高收入」，令男人唔揀佢地！<br />\n<br />\n成日發脾氣多多好男仔都比你激死<br />\n有咩好嬲？<br />\n<br />\n港女真係最憎運動<br />\n跑步減肥永遠得個講字，去gym room又要找男仔教佢做"},{"pid":"20b07da2df849f1cab06b359e6b1f9ff8767a842","tid":813684,"uid":195323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:46:38.000Z","msg":"巴打好勁"},{"pid":"a40916021862ca54e67bbe881818a5b1c7308653","tid":813684,"uid":195323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f12e16ec0ca5daa76c85eeabc34e286a11db182","tid":813684,"uid":195323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:47:23.000Z","msg":"正皮"},{"pid":"737572d6eee240c3edebc3ff02732de484efd01a","tid":813684,"uid":195323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:47:45.000Z","msg":"勁"},{"pid":"454aaa626d3601ab0724a5ec656c8e1b9fd70cc0","tid":813684,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:49:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f4d95d71f2baff281362d85b67901de625a8199","tid":813684,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:49:27.000Z","msg":"港男呢"},{"pid":"3ca3131bdd9ba825247ee0e2e5a36a98cfa7251b","tid":813684,"uid":208726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T15:51:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94535f0792d7dc4b6b2e8f9d80e72edafb4015fc","tid":813684,"uid":184233,"like"